node.text:
Love (Sweet Love) is OUT NOW 🍃🌻✨

Created by @sakimamusic @mnek @laurenaquilina @leighannepinnock and myself 🥰 with a gorgey sample of @morcheebaband ✨ 

Directed by the one and only @samuel.douek 🌙 

Serving you gag worthy harmonies and ad libs for days, this song is all about giving yourself that sweeeet lovinnnnnn however and whichever way pleases you best 👀🌼💥 Enjoy!

node.text:
10 years of @littlemix 🌌

Somewhere, in a parallel universe, I didn’t turn up to the audition that changed my life. I went for my plan B path because I thought music was too unrealistic. I didn’t have the confidence to believe I could truly do what I loved everyday. I’m grateful to my younger self for being brave enough to fight for her dreams. She has given me a music career I could only dream of, life long family and friends as well as the most phenomenal fan base. Little me is beaming 💫

Being in this group is my proudest achievement thus far. 

#10YearsOfLittleMix

node.text: Me and me Mam used to visit London once a year when I was little - we’d go to Madame Tussauds and she’d always say “you’ll be in here one day” 😭 What an unbelievable experience seeing how the amazing artists and team create these masterpieces! Thank you so much @madametussauds for making our dream a reality ✨ Last slide is the pose I requested but they turned it down 🤷🏽‍♀️
